 - 10:00-] &nbsp; %0a>>%3c%3c%0a(:if1 authgroup @tas:)%0a>>rfloat%3c%3c%0a{[foxdelrange button 210205-180014-664980 {$FullName} ]}%0a>>%3c%3c%0a(:if1end:)%0a!!!!!gabrielz%0a(:div1end:) %0a>>messageitem%3c%3c %0a'''My thoughts'''%0a>>messageitem%3c%3c%0aThere are lots of ways that writing systems come about, but this post brings to mind the Korean writing system, which was specifically created to be intuitive and easy to learn, in contrast to the previous way for writing Korean, which used the Chinese system, and thus was difficult to learn and use for Korean speakers. %0a>>%3c%3c%0a#foxend 210205-180014-664980#%0a%0a%0a%0a(:Section: :)%0a(:Category: PracticeCategory:)
